Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.85,0:00:04.95,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That child said he wanted to see the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.80,0:00:08.27,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I couldn't take him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.61,0:00:11.46,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There were so many things I wanted to do for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.48,0:00:14.55,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I couldn't do a single thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.78,0:00:19.11,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}even though the summer had just begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.20,0:00:39.13,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukito-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.29,0:00:42.01,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukito-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.29,0:00:43.02,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,it's morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.12,0:00:49.60,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.91,0:02:28.41,Air Typesetting,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs54\c&HB83D41&\pos(643,96)}Episode 5
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.15,0:02:40.18,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you glad Kirishima-san recovered?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.85,0:02:41.22,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.97,0:02:47.71,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, when I saw that feather, I also had a kinda mysterious feeling.
Comment: 0,0:02:48.49,0:02:50.17,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alt: I felt strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.98,0:02:50.70,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukito-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.09,0:02:52.64,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Did you say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.21,0:02:55.44,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been spaced out ever since you got up.
Comment: 0,0:02:54.49,0:02:55.44,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alt: woke up
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.94,0:02:56.49,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.80,0:02:58.77,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I had a dream of when I was a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.17,0:02:59.72,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.15,0:03:01.25,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing to worry about.
Comment: 0,0:03:00.14,0:03:01.26,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alt: It's no big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.97,0:03:04.45,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, are you still having those dreams?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.46,0:03:05.79,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.72,0:03:11.14,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Last night's dream was different from anything I've had before.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.85,0:03:14.25,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The moon was out and it was so bright.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.23,0:03:17.60,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was trying to fly up to the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.24,0:03:21.59,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was sore all over, but I kept trying to go higher and higher.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.27,0:03:24.32,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And then, I heard voices.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.76,0:03:25.04,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Voices?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.55,0:03:29.66,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The voices of many people, trying to restrain me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.25,0:03:34.50,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They echoed in my ears, so I couldn't climb anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.32,0:03:37.70,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'll see you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.05,0:03:38.36,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.76,0:03:40.71,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be going.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.35,0:03:42.39,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, be carefu-
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.33,0:03:42.59,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.66,0:03:47.24,Air Typesetting,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs40\pos(471,105)\c&H56177E&}LUNA'S
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.66,0:03:47.24,Air Typesetting,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs40\pos(743,106)\c&HBCB9DA&}BAR
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.66,0:03:47.24,Air Typesetting,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs36\c&HEBCA84&\pos(753,672)}Asahi
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.66,0:03:47.24,Air Typesetting,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs32\c&H0C0000&\pos(1069,430)}USED
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.66,0:03:47.24,Air Typesetting,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs32\c&H0C0000&\pos(1069,581)}BOOK
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.66,0:03:47.24,Air Typesetting,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs32\c&H0C0000&\pos(1069,718)}STORE
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.26,0:03:52.85,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.04,0:03:54.90,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's great, isn't it, Onee-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.28,0:03:59.26,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how it's walking without any strings.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.95,0:04:00.40,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.69,0:04:01.77,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It fell down.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.59,0:04:04.83,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It got up! It got up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.76,0:04:07.97,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That is the way kids should be.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.97,0:04:08.64,Air Dialogue - top,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko piko.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.15,0:04:12.43,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, shouldn't you be with Kano?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.07,0:04:10.26,Air Dialogue - top,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko?
Comment: 0,0:04:10.21,0:04:10.21,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alt: by Kano's side
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.63,0:04:13.95,Air Dialogue - top,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko piko piko.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.16,0:04:16.57,Air Dialogue - top,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko piko piko piko pikori.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.53,0:04:16.57,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, she went to school to take care of the animals today?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.18,0:04:19.73,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, why am I talking to you like it's normal?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.07,0:04:20.48,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.02,0:04:22.59,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, we have to go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.59,0:04:22.94,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.11,0:04:26.35,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Doll-san, see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.35,0:04:30.68,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shake hands, shake hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.03,0:04:31.42,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.55,0:04:31.85,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.29,0:04:38.83,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's what being "really close" is like, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.25,0:04:40.10,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Pikori.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.42,0:04:42.58,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't make any money again.
Comment: 0,0:04:43.03,0:04:49.42,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alt: I worked for free again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.15,0:04:51.15,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That Misuzu is late.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.61,0:04:55.92,Air Dialogue - top,,0000,0000,0000,,Munch munch munch.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.42,0:04:58.32,Air Dialogue - top,,0000,0000,0000,,Chew chew chew chew.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.53,0:05:01.25,Air Dialogue - top,,0000,0000,0000,,Mumchy munchy munchy munchy munchy munchy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.95,0:05:01.25,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Tohno.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.85,0:05:02.05,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.77,0:05:04.72,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Kunisaki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.17,0:05:06.09,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.69,0:05:06.06,Air Dialogue alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.45,0:05:09.44,Air Dialogue alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Wa hah hoo hooey hee?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.42,0:05:09.43,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're going to say something, swallow first.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.39,0:05:12.85,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.25,0:05:14.83,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You are welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.35,0:05:16.96,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you seen Misuzu?
Comment: 0,0:05:17.75,0:05:17.75,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alt: Did misuzu come this way?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.55,0:05:18.40,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kamio-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.09,0:05:19.50,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.94,0:05:20.33,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.00,0:05:21.60,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.93,0:05:24.37,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you make hamburgers tomorrow too?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.85,0:05:25.21,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.51,0:05:26.50,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.66,0:05:28.06,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What a little pig!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.71,0:05:36.97,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.07,0:05:38.82,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You let go first!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.51,0:05:42.43,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Michiru?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.92,0:05:45.24,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.16,0:06:05.16,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.16,0:06:05.16,Air Dialogue alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.95,0:06:07.28,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you able to use the shower?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.54,0:06:08.00,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.74,0:06:11.14,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you get the keys to this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.45,0:06:16.55,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My father was the stationmaster here,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.85,0:06:19.87,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but he's not working here anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.34,0:06:22.73,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he working somewhere else?
Comment: 0,0:06:23.31,0:06:24.78,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alt: Did he find a different job?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.54,0:06:25.33,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.55,0:06:28.81,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,As a token of apology, here.
