Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.76,0:06:33.30,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And today...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.86,0:06:34.45,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,this too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.03,0:06:38.20,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the bottle I found yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.32,0:06:40.86,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is startdust,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.33,0:06:45.85,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,sand grains shaped like baby stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.35,0:06:48.39,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, is it really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.45,0:06:48.93,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.54,0:06:51.46,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.84,0:06:53.69,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They rustle!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.00,0:06:55.45,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kunisaki-san too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.81,0:06:56.27,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.33,0:06:59.00,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can have one too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.25,0:06:59.73,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.08,0:07:01.56,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,With this, the three of us...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.67,0:07:03.34,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,match.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.80,0:07:14.35,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This sand was given to me by my father, when I was a little girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.78,0:07:16.81,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then isn't it something precious?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.95,0:07:18.40,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure about this?
Comment: 0,0:07:17.95,0:07:18.39,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alt: Is it all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.12,0:07:22.40,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, if it's Kunisaki-san and Michiru.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.48,0:07:29.57,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like Kamio-san has already left.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.10,0:07:31.01,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.46,0:07:35.88,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it possible she stayed at school this late?
Comment: 0,0:07:36.55,0:07:36.55,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Awkward phrashing maybe above?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.35,0:07:37.10,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.15,0:07:42.30,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Kunisaki-san, are you busy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.68,0:07:47.99,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome to the Astronomy Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.72,0:07:49.77,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.16,0:07:52.09,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The stars are already out!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.48,0:07:54.00,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are the other club members?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.95,0:07:56.67,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There are no others.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.18,0:07:59.33,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I am the only member.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.66,0:08:00.25,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The only?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.70,0:08:03.05,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'm club president.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.39,0:08:04.99,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a really selective club.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.99,0:08:05.82,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.19,0:08:15.10,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Does she come here often?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.00,0:08:19.20,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No. This is the first time I've brought her here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.73,0:08:22.23,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.75,0:08:26.60,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,you're not going out of your way to be here, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.86,0:08:27.32,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.79,0:08:29.69,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.91,0:08:36.55,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted the three of us to observe the stars together,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.34,0:08:41.01,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,because she seems to like you, Kunisaki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.36,0:08:43.01,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.40,0:08:43.93,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.41,0:08:50.60,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She talks about you constantly when she is with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.24,0:08:54.93,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She really likes you, Kunisaki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.04,0:08:56.70,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe that at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.27,0:08:59.02,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can tell how she feels,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.90,0:09:03.10,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,because she is my other half.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.64,0:09:04.21,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Other half?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.61,0:09:12.55,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Michiru and I have always spent our time together, like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.41,0:09:18.49,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So cute...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.98,0:09:19.22,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Blush.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.54,0:09:19.81,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.56,0:09:21.85,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kunisaki-san, you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.15,0:09:22.51,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.19,0:09:26.94,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,... always traveling alone, isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.56,0:09:31.00,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you ever spent time like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.07,0:09:35.81,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The happiness of spending time with someone else...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.52,0:09:39.66,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The joy of living for someone else's sake...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.30,0:09:43.79,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even someone like me should have done,
Comment: 0,0:09:42.90,0:09:43.77,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Done unnecessary?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.03,0:09:46.35,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,though it was a long, long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.33,0:09:49.09,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.41,0:09:51.78,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to go now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.02,0:09:53.57,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mm, see you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.80,0:09:55.85,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, then it's Michiru Dash!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.51,0:09:58.38,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.74,0:10:01.15,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to walk me home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.37,0:10:01.77,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.02,0:10:02.65,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.07,0:10:04.84,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're pretty tall.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.70,0:10:08.66,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you not like tall girls?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.71,0:10:09.07,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.50,0:10:11.50,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A good figure is an advantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.50,0:10:12.75,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Blush.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.61,0:10:17.44,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I happen to be rather proud of it myself too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.00,0:10:19.09,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Happen to be rather, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.43,0:10:20.28,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Happen to be.
Comment: 0,0:10:21.44,0:10:21.85,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Super awkward. Needs rephrasing I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.69,0:10:26.44,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The taller you are, the closer you are to the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.20,0:10:30.89,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for walking me home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.00,0:10:31.97,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mention it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.46,0:10:35.37,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please be careful walking home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.58,0:10:35.84,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.91,0:10:37.75,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.43,0:10:40.10,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, who are you with?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.88,0:10:43.53,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A new member of the Astronomy Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.53,0:10:44.18,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.98,0:10:47.55,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I remember you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.01,0:10:50.33,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much for helping me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.99,0:10:51.17,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.74,0:10:52.44,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.83,0:10:54.96,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I helped her with some heavy bags the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.51,0:10:59.35,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for having you go to the trouble of walking my daughter home.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.01,0:11:01.59,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, come on inside...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.87,0:11:02.40,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Michiru.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.61,0:11:06.79,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Michiru?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.16,0:11:09.41,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Dinner is already ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.88,0:11:12.27,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.85,0:11:15.72,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Tohno.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.44,0:11:16.33,Air Dialogue alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.60,0:11:26.22,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.08,0:11:32.29,Air Typesetting,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs12\frx350\fry356\frz3.964\pos(675,346)\c&H060607&}I'm\Ndoing my\Nhomework.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.90,0:11:36.46,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Misuzu,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.77,0:11:37.23,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming in.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.81,0:11:45.77,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.28,0:11:46.95,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll catch a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.74,0:11:52.42,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Yukito-san, good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.72,0:11:53.80,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's still night now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.30,0:11:57.21,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You should have told me you had to stay late at supplemental classes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.17,0:12:00.70,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.38,0:12:02.77,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez... Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.75,0:12:05.15,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.21,0:12:07.80,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you keeping a picture diary?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.76,0:12:09.07,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.40,0:12:11.29,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my choice of assignment for the summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.66,0:12:14.61,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Maestro!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.05,0:12:16.95,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you betray me?!
Comment: 0,0:12:14.43,0:12:17.13,Air Typesetting,,0000,0000,0000,,Kids! Please watch this show in a bright room,
Comment: 0,0:12:17.40,0:12:18.47,Air Typesetting,,0000,0000,0000,,And make sure to sit far from the TV!
Comment: 0,0:12:15.13,0:12:17.13,Air Typesetting,,0000,0000,0000,,Unedited Typesetting. I think not to include it tbh.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.02,0:12:17.96,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.20,0:12:20.89,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You think you can conduct this orchestra?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.03,0:12:22.05,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What a joke!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.49,0:12:22.83,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.40,0:12:25.31,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If I don't conduct, who will?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.89,0:12:26.99,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Give the baton to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.98,0:12:29.94,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The only way you'll get it is over my dead body!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.31,0:12:32.80,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.99,0:12:34.25,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Appassionato God Fingers!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.60,0:12:38.62,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Geh! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.89,0:12:40.68,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That was the best part!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.40,0:12:45.53,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's play cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.17,0:12:49.72,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're really persistent.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.22,0:12:52.70,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I just want to play cards with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.28,0:12:55.64,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.87,0:12:56.74,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.31,0:12:58.10,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.10,0:12:59.51,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.10,0:13:03.79,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'll play with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.91,0:13:06.45,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.80,0:13:07.99,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what do you want to play?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.24,0:13:08.88,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Old Maid?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.15,0:13:09.65,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Poker?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.74,0:13:12.26,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Make it something simple that doesn't require thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.25,0:13:15.75,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay then, let's play Concentration.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.13,0:13:24.44,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.27,0:13:25.50,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.30,0:13:26.69,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.16,0:13:27.33,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.14,0:13:30.51,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.35,0:13:33.47,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I messed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.85,0:13:44.63,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.82,0:13:45.95,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm not crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.50,0:13:51.20,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can play.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.02,0:13:55.36,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to try my hardest.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.34,0:13:57.60,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to try my hardest.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.37,0:13:59.08,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.35,0:14:00.67,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you not feeling well?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.07,0:14:01.87,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.03,0:14:03.88,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.46,0:14:08.90,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Misuzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.45,0:14:10.05,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.32,0:14:10.66,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.47,0:14:12.17,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Get a hold of yourself!
Comment: 0,0:14:11.47,0:14:12.16,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alt: Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.50,0:14:15.89,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Misuzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.20,0:14:18.17,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Misuzu suddenly–
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.16,0:14:18.86,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.47,0:14:21.09,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you mind stepping outside for a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.87,0:14:22.30,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Misuzu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.65,0:14:23.65,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down, Misuzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.71,0:14:43.73,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's been like this ever since she was a little girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.71,0:14:47.62,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She becomes like that, right when she's about to make a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.32,0:14:50.25,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right when she's about to make a friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.71,0:14:54.70,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've had the doctor at the clinic look at her, and I've even tried going to a big hospital,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.51,0:14:56.40,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but it was no use.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.25,0:15:01.74,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They all said it was probably only psychological and she'd grow out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.87,0:15:06.32,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She actually had an episode at school today too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.72,0:15:10.06,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They called me at work, so I went to pick her up on my bike,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.45,0:15:12.24,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and brought her straight home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.75,0:15:13.31,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.88,0:15:19.15,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was expecting and hoping that she'd be all right with you,
Comment: 0,0:15:20.50,0:15:21.28,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Awkard phrase above.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.12,0:15:23.57,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,since she's all right when she's with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.74,0:15:35.21,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really leaving?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.90,0:15:38.35,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She'll suffer these attacks as long as I'm here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.03,0:15:40.14,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I should keep my distance for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.42,0:15:42.10,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.93,0:15:48.71,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell her that I'll still keep walking her to and from school, just like before.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.85,0:15:51.69,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Come over for dinner every now and then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.11,0:16:05.73,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my fault that you weren't able to stay at my house.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.11,0:16:07.99,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you lonely living by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.54,0:16:12.29,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I'm living alone, I've made quite a few friends somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.34,0:16:15.75,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You have some friends too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.20,0:16:16.80,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.14,0:16:17.81,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm always alone,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.07,0:16:22.63,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,because whenever I'm about to make a friend, I start crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.96,0:16:24.95,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone always runs away from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.26,0:16:27.61,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But you have Haruko, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.84,0:16:28.56,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.60,0:16:30.66,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's not my real mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.62,0:16:35.46,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.70,0:16:39.66,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruko-san is actually my aunt.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.96,0:16:42.65,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was dumped onto her because I was such a strange kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.20,0:16:48.96,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruko-san didn't want me, but in the end, I had to live here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.42,0:16:52.32,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Since I don't want to cause her trouble,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.62,0:16:55.50,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,we live our separate lives under one roof.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.55,0:16:57.91,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I don't say anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.52,0:17:03.11,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a real burden on her, and I don't want to be any more trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.43,0:17:08.50,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, I play by myself, looking for weird juices, or playing cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.15,0:17:12.70,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Misuzu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.97,0:17:13.25,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.71,0:17:15.86,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Just keep smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.05,0:17:20.26,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,V!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.75,0:17:23.48,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay then, see you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.98,0:17:24.60,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.97,0:17:29.40,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.65,0:17:33.42,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Minagi hasn't come.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.85,0:17:34.85,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's at school, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.37,0:17:36.08,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She'll be here soon.
Comment: 0,0:17:35.38,0:17:36.08,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,alt: eventually
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.17,0:17:40.20,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's not supposed to be at school today.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.29,0:17:53.29,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I do something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.31,0:17:56.26,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me that for a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.30,0:17:56.84,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.77,0:17:58.89,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.89,0:17:59.80,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Just watch, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.80,0:18:00.58,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.57,0:18:02.25,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an indirect kiss!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.26,0:18:03.30,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.30,0:18:04.40,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't talk about adult stuff!
Comment: 0,0:18:03.31,0:18:04.40,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,awkard phrasing maybe
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.49,0:18:08.89,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.75,0:18:13.88,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That was amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.09,0:18:15.31,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.08,0:18:20.20,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.18,0:18:22.42,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.85,0:18:25.48,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Bubbles are so pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.30,0:18:28.84,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They're empty, just like the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.55,0:18:32.36,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She didn't come.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.77,0:18:33.57,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, she didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.62,0:18:36.70,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if something happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.14,0:18:41.12,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's try going to her house.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.96,0:18:43.63,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Minagi's house?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.96,0:18:44.44,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.97,0:18:46.68,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If she isn't coming, then we should go visit her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.77,0:18:49.10,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.42,0:18:52.55,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to go to her house.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.03,0:18:53.92,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're her friend, right?
Comment: 0,0:18:54.45,0:18:55.40,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alt: You're friends, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.45,0:18:55.40,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You've never been?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.35,0:18:58.84,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll go by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.33,0:19:01.30,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to pick up Misuzu too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.72,0:19:02.07,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.54,0:19:05.28,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for walking me home.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.54,0:19:07.50,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but I can't stay today.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.13,0:19:10.02,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not eating dinner with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.31,0:19:11.32,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have somewhere to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.65,0:19:12.30,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,See you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.04,0:19:13.42,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.83,0:19:21.07,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.55,0:19:22.70,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I met you yesterday, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.04,0:19:24.54,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the new member of the Astronomy Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.07,0:19:25.35,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.98,0:19:27.08,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm running an errand.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.52,0:19:29.01,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,May I see your daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.54,0:19:30.30,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.99,0:19:31.75,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Has she gone somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.45,0:19:34.50,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have a daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.73,0:19:35.02,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.58,0:19:37.39,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure you've got the right address?
Comment: 0,0:19:38.71,0:19:38.71,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alt: address -> house
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.76,0:19:37.93,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.15,0:19:39.47,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.77,0:19:40.57,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're kidding me, right?
Comment: 0,0:19:41.78,0:19:41.78,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alt: You're joking
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.57,0:19:41.00,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.61,0:19:44.20,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here, skipping work?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.74,0:19:49.63,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Tohno-san's mother has been suffering a psychological disorder.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.50,0:19:53.04,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been checking on her every time I get a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.31,0:19:56.92,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She convinced herself that her elder daughter, Minagi-san, is her younger daughter,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.92,0:19:58.57,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,the one who passed away.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.47,0:20:00.69,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She believed that for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.91,0:20:04.75,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But it seems her condition has suddenly changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.93,0:20:08.61,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When she accepted the fact that her younger daughter was dead,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.19,0:20:10.24,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,she erased Minagi-san from her mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.79,0:20:16.98,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In her mind, neither one of her daughters ever existed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.21,0:20:33.17,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was supposed to have a little sister, named Michiru,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.40,0:20:34.83,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,a precious little sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.41,0:20:41.93,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My mother was sad because I was close to my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.15,0:20:48.27,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The baby she was expecting was supposed to fill the hole in her heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.42,0:20:53.76,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you could have just one dream come true, what would it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.35,0:20:56.89,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm... Ummm...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.55,0:20:58.89,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I want a little sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.89,0:21:02.55,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My mother couldn't accept the reality,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.55,0:21:06.26,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,so she chose to live in her dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.99,0:21:10.33,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And I became a fragment of that dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.90,0:21:16.32,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But last night, she saw herself in a dream having a miscarriage of Michiru.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.07,0:21:22.00,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,According to Kirishima-sensei, that made my mother accept the reality.
Comment: 0,0:21:22.94,0:21:24.61,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alt: My mother accepted the reality after seeing that
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.41,0:21:27.52,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This morning, when she saw me, my mother said,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.30,0:21:29.55,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"Who are you?"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.17,0:21:33.18,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't go back?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.90,0:21:37.45,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the end of my dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.74,0:21:44.06,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It is the end of my dream, in which I lived as Michiru.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.19,0:21:50.43,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My wings have forgotten how to fly,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.70,0:21:57.05,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,because I always just pretended to fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.02,0:22:02.83,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there a use for wings that cannot fly?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.96,0:23:42.73,Air Typesetting,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&\fad(300,900)\fs51\shad2.25\pos(641,293)}Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.15,0:23:42.15,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.40,0:23:45.17,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you're more suited to travel than I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.02,0:23:47.57,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you come with me, Tohno?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.95,0:23:48.30,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.27,0:23:51.83,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Something has to change.
Comment: 0,0:23:49.57,0:23:51.57,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alt: It's not good being like this after all. Context: Minagi has to wake up from her dream
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.70,0:23:57.31,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to show you the world;
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.87,0:23:59.89,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,the real world, not a dream world.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.30,0:24:07.01,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything started with my sin...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.83,0:24:20.14,Air Typesetting,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(950,0)\fs39\fscx100\fscy100\shad2.4\c&HFEFEFA&\4c&H121213&\pos(956,419)}Episode 6
